---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="服務項目 | 凝膠美甲・手足保養・穿戴甲・美甲教學" description="伊特美甲提供台北中山區凝膠美甲、光療延甲、手足保養、穿戴甲訂製與日式美甲教學。立即預約享新客優惠。">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-8 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <nav class="text-sm text-it-text mb-4"><a href="/" class="hover:text-it-cta">首頁</a> <span class="mx-2">/</span> <span>服務項目</span></nav>
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">伊特美甲服務項目</h1>
        <p class="text-it-text max-w-2xl mx-auto">從日常凝膠美甲到專業美甲教學，提供全方位的指尖美學服務。台北中山區美甲推薦首選。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">凝膠美甲</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">專業光療凝膠技術，色彩飽和持久，呵護您的天然指甲。包含前置保養、凝膠上色、建構加固。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>單色凝膠</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,200 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>貓眼 / 漸層</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,500 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>設計款</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">依複雜度報價</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/pricing" class="text-it-cta font-medium hover:text-it-dark transition-colors">查看完整價格表 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">光療延甲</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">硬式凝膠延甲技術，改善甲型問題，打造完美長度與弧度。適合指甲較短或甲型不整者。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>單指延甲</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$150</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>全手延甲</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,500 起</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/pricing" class="text-it-cta font-medium hover:text-it-dark transition-colors">查看完整價格表 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">手足保養</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">深層滋養與角質護理，讓雙手雙足恢復細緻柔嫩。使用專業級保養產品。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>手部基礎保養</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$800</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>足部基礎保養</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,000</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>深層護理療程</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,500</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/pricing" class="text-it-cta font-medium hover:text-it-dark transition-colors">查看完整價格表 →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">穿戴甲訂製</h2>
          <p class="text-it-text mb-4">量身訂製的時尚穿戴甲，隨時變換風格。附贈專用果凍膠與收納盒。</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-it-text space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>基礎款</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,000 起</span></li>
            <li class="flex justify-between"><span>設計款</span><span class="font-bold text-it-cta">NT$1,500 起</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/pricing" class="text-it-cta font-medium hover:text-it-dark transition-colors">查看完整價格表 →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
